# TODO - Image-to-Image Migration

**Project**: Migrate txt-to-img tool to img-to-img processing with Markdown input files

**PRD Reference**: `USER-FILES/00.KB/prd.md`

---

## Project Setup

### Environment & Dependencies
- [ ] Verify all required packages installed in venv (replicate, pyyaml, loguru, rich, natsort, Pillow)
- [ ] Confirm 1Password CLI authentication working for REPLICATE_API_TOKEN
- [ ] Verify `run.py` wrapper script handles environment setup correctly

