## Phase 4: Output Filename Migration

### Update Output Writer
- [ ] Modify `src/output/writer.py` output filename generation
  - Change from `{filename}_{profile}_{timestamp}.png` pattern
  - Change to `{timestamp}_{filename}.png` pattern
  - Example: `250131_143052_example1.png`
  - Ensure timestamp format is YYMMDD_HHMMSS
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 06.1, 04.7

- [ ] Verify output directory structure creates per-file subfolders
  - Pattern: `05.OUTPUT/{YYMMDD_HHMMSS}/{markdown_filename}/`
  - Each markdown file gets own subfolder with image + logs
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.3

