## Phase 7: Testing & Validation

### Manual Testing Checklist
- [ ] Test Case 1: Parse example1.md successfully
  - Verify image URL extraction: `https://f003.backblazeb2.com/file/isof-bucket/batch6_upscaled/prompt09.0.png`
  - Verify prompt extraction: "A man carries heavy bags on a ship dock."
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 07.2

- [ ] Test Case 2: Build payload with profile image_input (2 URLs in array)
  - Use nano-banano-pro_9x16_2k_RUBEN.yaml profile
  - Verify image_input array has 2 elements
  - Verify prompt has suffix applied
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 07.3

- [ ] Test Case 3: Build payload without profile image_input (1 URL in array)
  - Use profile without image_input field
  - Verify image_input array has 1 element (still array, not string)
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.2

- [ ] Test Case 4: Verify prompt prefix/suffix application
  - Test with both prefix and suffix
  - Test with only suffix
  - Test with neither (verbatim markdown text)
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.2

- [ ] Test Case 5: Error handling - missing image URL
  - Create markdown file without `![image](URL)` syntax
  - Verify script fails fast with message "No image URL found in {filename}.md"
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.4

- [ ] Test Case 6: Error handling - missing code block
  - Create markdown file without code block
  - Verify script fails fast with message "No prompt text found in {filename}.md"
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.4

- [ ] Test Case 7: Error handling - empty code block
  - Create markdown file with empty code block
  - Verify script fails fast with message "Empty prompt in {filename}.md"
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.4

- [ ] Test Case 8: Output filename verification
  - Run script and verify output named `YYMMDD_HHMMSS_example1.png`
  - Verify no profile name in filename
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 04.7

- [ ] Test Case 9: Output directory structure
  - Verify timestamped folder created: `05.OUTPUT/YYMMDD_HHMMSS/`
  - Verify per-file subfolder: `05.OUTPUT/YYMMDD_HHMMSS/example1/`
  - Verify logs in correct location
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.3

- [ ] Test Case 10: Matrix processing with multiple files and profiles
  - Place 2 markdown files in 04.INPUT/
  - Ensure 2 profiles in 03.PROFILES/
  - Verify 4 total operations (2 × 2)
  - Verify natural sorting of markdown files
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.3

- [ ] Test Case 11: Rate limiting
  - Verify delay_between_requests from profile is respected
  - Test with profile having delay_between_requests: 2.0
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.3

- [ ] Test Case 12: Summary log generation
  - Verify summary markdown file created with correct format
  - Check all required sections present (Input, Processing, Output, Notes)
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.5

- [ ] Test Case 13: Failure log generation
  - Force an API error (invalid model_id)
  - Verify FAILURE.md created with error details
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 05.5

- [ ] Test Case 14: Confirm no .txt file processing
  - Place .txt file in 04.INPUT/
  - Verify script ignores it completely
  - **PRD Reference**: Section 01.3

