## Future Enhancements (Not for Current Implementation)

**These items are explicitly excluded from the current migration per PRD Section 09:**

- Multiple image support per markdown file (current: first image only)
- Different output formats beyond PNG (current: PNG only)
- Parallel/concurrent processing (current: sequential only)
- Configurable retry logic in profiles (current: hardcoded)
- Custom output naming templates (current: fixed format)
- Dry-run mode for testing without API calls
- Cross-run cost reporting and analytics
- Auto-archiving processed files to 06.DONE/
- Extended markdown validation (URL accessibility checks, etc.)
- Local image file support (current: URLs only)
- Batch size limiting or pagination
- Progress persistence and resume capability
- Webhook notifications on completion
- Multi-model comparison features

**Remember**: Make it work. Keep it simple. Move on.

